		<title>狗狗狂掉毛到崩潰？這5個「日常習慣」讓掉毛減少又健康 !</title>
		<link>https://firenews.com.tw/2025/08/02/%e7%8b%97%e7%8b%97%e7%8b%82%e6%8e%89%e6%af%9b%e5%88%b0%e5%b4%a9%e6%bd%b0%ef%bc%9f%e9%80%995%e5%80%8b%e3%80%8c%e6%97%a5%e5%b8%b8%e7%bf%92%e6%85%a3%e3%80%8d%e8%ae%93%e6%8e%89%e6%af%9b%e6%b8%9b%e5%b0%91/</link>
		
		<dc:creator><![CDATA[火報 時事新聞]]></dc:creator>
		<pubDate>Sat, 02 Aug 2025 07:30:02 +0000</pubDate>
				<category><![CDATA[新寵]]></category>
