					<description><![CDATA[<p><img width="2560" height="1707" src="https://firenews.com.tw/wp-content/uploads/2025/08/diana-parkhouse-h5qhJGNfhiY-unsplash-scaled.jpg" class="attachment-post-thumbnail size-post-thumbnail wp-post-image" alt="" decoding="async" srcset="https://i0.wp.com/firenews.com.tw/wp-content/uploads/2025/08/diana-parkhouse-h5qhJGNfhiY-unsplash-scaled.jpg?w=2560&amp;ssl=1 2560w, https://i0.wp.com/firenews.com.tw/wp-content/uploads/2025/08/diana-parkhouse-h5qhJGNfhiY-unsplash-scaled.jpg?resize=768%2C512&amp;ssl=1 768w, https://i0.wp.com/firenews.com.tw/wp-content/uploads/2025/08/diana-parkhouse-h5qhJGNfhiY-unsplash-scaled.jpg?resize=1536%2C1024&amp;ssl=1 1536w, https://i0.wp.com/firenews.com.tw/wp-content/uploads/2025/08/diana-parkhouse-h5qhJGNfhiY-unsplash-scaled.jpg?resize=2048%2C1365&amp;ssl=1 2048w, https://i0.wp.com/firenews.com.tw/wp-content/uploads/2025/08/diana-parkhouse-h5qhJGNfhiY-unsplash-scaled.jpg?resize=219%2C146&amp;ssl=1 219w, https://i0.wp.com/firenews.com.tw/wp-content/uploads/2025/08/diana-parkhouse-h5qhJGNfhiY-unsplash-scaled.jpg?w=2440&amp;ssl=1 2440w" sizes="(max-width: 2560px) 100vw, 2560px" /></p>
<p>火報記者 洪瑜蓉 / 綜合報導 最近一隻高齡巴哥犬因為太會賴床意外掀起網路話題，這隻狗狗即使已經睡了將近一整天 &#8230;</p>
<p>這篇文章 <a href="https://firenews.com.tw/2025/08/01/%e5%b0%b1%e6%98%af%e6%84%9b%e7%9d%a1%e8%a6%ba%ef%bc%81%e8%b3%b4%e5%ba%8a%e5%b7%b4%e5%93%a5%e7%8a%ac%e7%9d%a1%e4%ba%86%e4%b8%80%e6%95%b4%e5%a4%a9-%e7%b6%b2%e5%8f%8b%e7%ac%91%e7%a8%b1%ef%bc%9a%e6%a0%b9/">就是愛睡覺！賴床巴哥犬睡了一整天 網友笑稱：根本是我 </a> 最早出現於 <a href="https://firenews.com.tw">火報</a>。</p>
]]></description>
										<content:encoded><![CDATA[<p><img width="2560" height="1707" src="https://firenews.com.tw/wp-content/uploads/2025/08/diana-parkhouse-h5qhJGNfhiY-unsplash-scaled.jpg" class="attachment-post-thumbnail size-post-thumbnail wp-post-image" alt="" decoding="async" srcset="https://i0.wp.com/firenews.com.tw/wp-content/uploads/2025/08/diana-parkhouse-h5qhJGNfhiY-unsplash-scaled.jpg?w=2560&amp;ssl=1 2560w, https://i0.wp.com/firenews.com.tw/wp-content/uploads/2025/08/diana-parkhouse-h5qhJGNfhiY-unsplash-scaled.jpg?resize=768%2C512&amp;ssl=1 768w, https://i0.wp.com/firenews.com.tw/wp-content/uploads/2025/08/diana-parkhouse-h5qhJGNfhiY-unsplash-scaled.jpg?resize=1536%2C1024&amp;ssl=1 1536w, https://i0.wp.com/firenews.com.tw/wp-content/uploads/2025/08/diana-parkhouse-h5qhJGNfhiY-unsplash-scaled.jpg?resize=2048%2C1365&amp;ssl=1 2048w, https://i0.wp.com/firenews.com.tw/wp-content/uploads/2025/08/diana-parkhouse-h5qhJGNfhiY-unsplash-scaled.jpg?resize=219%2C146&amp;ssl=1 219w, https://i0.wp.com/firenews.com.tw/wp-content/uploads/2025/08/diana-parkhouse-h5qhJGNfhiY-unsplash-scaled.jpg?w=2440&amp;ssl=1 2440w" sizes="(max-width: 2560px) 100vw, 2560px" /></p>
<p>火報記者 洪瑜蓉 / 綜合報導</p>



<p>最近一隻高齡巴哥犬因為太會賴床意外掀起網路話題，這隻狗狗即使已經睡了將近一整天，主人卻怎麼叫都還不願意起身，可愛又懶惰的模樣引發大批網友共鳴，讓不少網友笑稱「天阿這根本完全就是我本人」。&nbsp;</p>



<p>據了解，這隻超級會賴床的狗狗名字叫做「馬卡羅尼娜（Macaronina）」是一隻已經高齡13歲的巴哥犬，從小最大的興趣就是睡覺，而這個嗜好隨著年紀增長後變本加厲，幾乎可以睡將近整整一天都不用起床。</p>



<figure class="wp-block-image size-full"><img decoding="async" width="1220" height="915" src="https://i0.wp.com/firenews.com.tw/wp-content/uploads/2025/08/joshua-fernandez-zNtuI2QzdFY-unsplash-scaled.jpg?resize=1220%2C915&#038;ssl=1" alt="" class="wp-image-235125" srcset="https://i0.wp.com/firenews.com.tw/wp-content/uploads/2025/08/joshua-fernandez-zNtuI2QzdFY-unsplash-scaled.jpg?w=2560&amp;ssl=1 2560w, https://i0.wp.com/firenews.com.tw/wp-content/uploads/2025/08/joshua-fernandez-zNtuI2QzdFY-unsplash-scaled.jpg?resize=768%2C576&amp;ssl=1 768w, https://i0.wp.com/firenews.com.tw/wp-content/uploads/2025/08/joshua-fernandez-zNtuI2QzdFY-unsplash-scaled.jpg?resize=1536%2C1152&amp;ssl=1 1536w, https://i0.wp.com/firenews.com.tw/wp-content/uploads/2025/08/joshua-fernandez-zNtuI2QzdFY-unsplash-scaled.jpg?resize=2048%2C1536&amp;ssl=1 2048w, https://i0.wp.com/firenews.com.tw/wp-content/uploads/2025/08/joshua-fernandez-zNtuI2QzdFY-unsplash-scaled.jpg?resize=195%2C146&amp;ssl=1 195w, https://i0.wp.com/firenews.com.tw/wp-content/uploads/2025/08/joshua-fernandez-zNtuI2QzdFY-unsplash-scaled.jpg?w=2440&amp;ssl=1 2440w" sizes="(max-width: 1220px) 100vw, 1220px" data-recalc-dims="1" /><figcaption class="wp-element-caption">「馬卡羅尼娜」即使被主人叫醒，也會立刻趴回原地繼續睡覺<br>(示意圖/Unsplash) </figcaption></figure>



<p>飼主透露，每當早上試圖叫醒愛犬時，「馬卡羅尼娜」總是眼皮沉重地瞇著眼睛，整個身體癱軟在床上，彷彿完全不受外界影響，即使自己伸手將牠抱起來放直，狗狗也只會「立刻軟回去」再度趴下接著睡。&nbsp;</p>



<p>狗狗每天睡眼惺忪、身體軟趴趴的模樣讓飼主哭笑不得，故事曝光也立刻吸引網友們的熱烈討論，不少人感到超有共鳴「就是我本人」、「完全能理解」、「高齡狗狗真的超會睡」、「我的日常寫照狗狗翻版」、「好療癒的感覺」。&nbsp;</p>
<p>這篇文章 <a href="https://firenews.com.tw/2025/08/01/%e5%b0%b1%e6%98%af%e6%84%9b%e7%9d%a1%e8%a6%ba%ef%bc%81%e8%b3%b4%e5%ba%8a%e5%b7%b4%e5%93%a5%e7%8a%ac%e7%9d%a1%e4%ba%86%e4%b8%80%e6%95%b4%e5%a4%a9-%e7%b6%b2%e5%8f%8b%e7%ac%91%e7%a8%b1%ef%bc%9a%e6%a0%b9/">就是愛睡覺！賴床巴哥犬睡了一整天 網友笑稱：根本是我 </a> 最早出現於 <a href="https://firenews.com.tw">火報</a>。</p>
]]></content:encoded>
					
		
		
