										<content:encoded><![CDATA[<p><img width="2560" height="1694" src="https://firenews.com.tw/wp-content/uploads/2025/08/marques-kaspbrak-n1amn-SHKzw-unsplash-scaled.jpg" class="attachment-post-thumbnail size-post-thumbnail wp-post-image" alt="" decoding="async" srcset="https://i0.wp.com/firenews.com.tw/wp-content/uploads/2025/08/marques-kaspbrak-n1amn-SHKzw-unsplash-scaled.jpg?w=2560&amp;ssl=1 2560w, https://i0.wp.com/firenews.com.tw/wp-content/uploads/2025/08/marques-kaspbrak-n1amn-SHKzw-unsplash-scaled.jpg?resize=768%2C508&amp;ssl=1 768w, https://i0.wp.com/firenews.com.tw/wp-content/uploads/2025/08/marques-kaspbrak-n1amn-SHKzw-unsplash-scaled.jpg?resize=1536%2C1016&amp;ssl=1 1536w, https://i0.wp.com/firenews.com.tw/wp-content/uploads/2025/08/marques-kaspbrak-n1amn-SHKzw-unsplash-scaled.jpg?resize=2048%2C1355&amp;ssl=1 2048w, https://i0.wp.com/firenews.com.tw/wp-content/uploads/2025/08/marques-kaspbrak-n1amn-SHKzw-unsplash-scaled.jpg?resize=221%2C146&amp;ssl=1 221w, https://i0.wp.com/firenews.com.tw/wp-content/uploads/2025/08/marques-kaspbrak-n1amn-SHKzw-unsplash-scaled.jpg?w=2440&amp;ssl=1 2440w" sizes="(max-width: 2560px) 100vw, 2560px" /></p>
<p>火報記者 洪瑜蓉 / 綜合報導</p>



<p>你有看過這麼愛看電視的小貓嗎？國外一隻熱愛看電視的貓咪，某日因為發現電視機突然被移走，露出失落又錯愕的神情，引起網友熱烈討論，不少人表示心疼，紛紛暴動抗議飼主「趕快把電視放回原位！」，意外掀起網上話題。&nbsp;</p>



<p>原來小貓的飼主平時就習慣讓愛貓一起坐在沙發上看電視，他經常會播放動物紀錄片、小短片等這類節目，而貓咪每次也都全神貫注地看著螢幕，看得十分津津有味、目不轉睛，彷彿成了「電視重度使用者」。&nbsp;</p>



<figure class="wp-block-image size-full"><img decoding="async" width="1220" height="915" src="https://i0.wp.com/firenews.com.tw/wp-content/uploads/2025/08/rosea-creates-EpdxBIsajEg-unsplash-scaled.jpg?resize=1220%2C915&#038;ssl=1" alt="" class="wp-image-235127" srcset="https://i0.wp.com/firenews.com.tw/wp-content/uploads/2025/08/rosea-creates-EpdxBIsajEg-unsplash-scaled.jpg?w=2560&amp;ssl=1 2560w, https://i0.wp.com/firenews.com.tw/wp-content/uploads/2025/08/rosea-creates-EpdxBIsajEg-unsplash-scaled.jpg?resize=768%2C576&amp;ssl=1 768w, https://i0.wp.com/firenews.com.tw/wp-content/uploads/2025/08/rosea-creates-EpdxBIsajEg-unsplash-scaled.jpg?resize=1536%2C1152&amp;ssl=1 1536w, https://i0.wp.com/firenews.com.tw/wp-content/uploads/2025/08/rosea-creates-EpdxBIsajEg-unsplash-scaled.jpg?resize=2048%2C1536&amp;ssl=1 2048w, https://i0.wp.com/firenews.com.tw/wp-content/uploads/2025/08/rosea-creates-EpdxBIsajEg-unsplash-scaled.jpg?resize=195%2C146&amp;ssl=1 195w, https://i0.wp.com/firenews.com.tw/wp-content/uploads/2025/08/rosea-creates-EpdxBIsajEg-unsplash-scaled.jpg?w=2440&amp;ssl=1 2440w" sizes="(max-width: 1220px) 100vw, 1220px" data-recalc-dims="1" /><figcaption class="wp-element-caption">貓咪每天都會坐在沙發上，全神貫注地盯著螢幕，看得十分津津有味<br>(示意圖/Unsplash)</figcaption></figure>



<p>日前飼主突發奇想，決定重新佈置室內空間，於是先將電視暫時移走，卻沒想到小貓發現電視不見後，頓時陷入極大混亂與失落，反覆確認原本的位置、低頭盯著空牆，彷彿無法接受自己最愛的電視忽然消失。&nbsp;</p>



<p>飼主將愛貓的有趣反應分享至網路上，迅速引起網上熱議，大批網友在底下紛紛留言「快點還牠電視」、「貓貓是無辜的」、「怎麼可以沒告訴牠就搬走」、「小貓只是想追劇」、「好可憐」、「貓奴們要暴動啦」、「抗議抗議」。&nbsp;</p>
